lyrics:
[Verse]
Mercury man in his rocket ship
Strumming his banjo, with a cosmic grip
He leads his space band, fearless and brave
Against capitalism's relentless wave

[Chorus]
They fight for freedom, they fight for peace
Their bluegrass tunes never cease
Together they'll rise, against the pain
Mercury man and his cosmic train
style: start the record with the most huge bass kick you ever done, after 4 kicks and a huge melodic in background
